Package org.jtool.pdg

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CallEdge
    An edge that represents a relationship between caller and callee in ClDGs and SDGs.
    CD
    An edge represents control dependence (CD) between PDG nodes.
    ClassMemberEdge
    An edge that represents a class and its members in ClDGs.
    ClDG
    An object storing information on a class dependence graph (ClDG).
    CommonPDG
    An object storing information on a program dependence graph (PDG).
    DD
    An edge that represents data dependence (DD) between PDG nodes.
    Dependence
    A dependence edge of PDGs, ClDGs, and SDGs.
    PDG
    An object storing information on a program dependence graph (PDG).
    PDGClassEntry
    The entry node for a ClDG for a class or an interface.
    PDGEntry
    The entry node for a PDG or a ClDG.
    PDGNode
    A node of PDGs, ClDGs, and SDG.
    PDGStatement
    A statement node of a PDG, which stores defined and used variables.
    SDG
    An object storing information on a system dependence graph (SDG).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Dependence.Kind
    The kind of a dependence edge.
